column_.text_: Wow... This part of the sky is full of islands.

Indeed. They form the archipelago, and one of them is home to
Folca.
So this other island we're flying to... Will we be arriving soon?

Yes, we'll be there shortly. I just hope the islanders are evacuating
as we speak.
You said we're going to Tempeal, right? What kind of place is it?

It's a bustling mining village. All the rare metals they dig up put
them on the map.
What...

Does anyone else see that? I mean the wind around the island. You
can actually see it!
Huh, yeah! Why's it all weird?

The gales are reaching us from this distance? I suppose that
confirms my suspicions.
The wind's gettin' worse! Feel's like the ship's gonna snap in half!

Ahh... Good technique! Only a pro would turn starboard to
stabilize the ship.

I'll set her down a bit farther from the mines! It's about to get
bumpy!
Everyone! Grab on to somethin'!
What a ride. My life flashed before my eyes.
There should be more people here...
Rolan. We should talk...

I see. The abnormal winds agitated the goblins, who in turn
attacked the islanders.

We managed to escape, but the others... I pray the worst hasn't
befallen them.
Try not to worry too much. Just leave everything to Mr. Fix It!
Thank you. I'll go spread the word!
That being said, I can't just leave these people here unprotected.
What should I do—
He needs our aid, .
Did somebody call for goblin exterminators?
We'll handle the goblins.
We'll handle the goblins.
You focus on the evacuees.
We'll handle the goblins.
We'll handle the goblins.
Are you sure? That'd certainly take a load off my shoulders!
Talk about having the right crew for the job. Thanks a lot!
You focus on the evacuees.
You focus on the evacuees.
We'll find those stragglers!
Great! Thanks for the help. I'm counting on you guys.
I'll come find you after I get all these people aboard the airship.

If you happen to see any more islanders out there, could you give
them assistance?
Yep, you got it!
Oh, I almost forgot to give you this.

If anything happens, we can communicate with each other using
this device.
We can talk on this thing? Looks like a flower glued to a box.
It's a type of transceiver. It'll allow us to talk over long distances.

Aren't transceivers expensive? Are you sure you want to give us
one?
Yep, don't worry. I didn't pay for it since I put it together myself.
Check this out. It even has a nifty light attachment.

Why don't you turn it on, Vyrn, when you want to grab everyone's
attention? Might come in handy!
Nice... You got skills, Fix It Dude!
It's Rolan.
Who'da thunk you could make sweet gizmos like this?
Thank you. We'll definitely make good use of it!
Follow that road, and it'll take you to Tempeal.
Please help anyone you see! I'm counting on you!
Move it, people! Double time!
I'll lead the way! Let's go!
Ready when you are.
Come on, everyone! Follow me!
First day in this skydom, and we're already hard at work.
I don't like this feeling. Let's all be careful now.
Everything here is new to us. Stay on your guard.

I'm concerned for those who couldn't evacuate. We'd best
hurry!
Are we all set to go? Make sure you don't forget anything!

The situation is in my hands. Summon me immediately for
assistance.
Allow me to carve a path forward.
Captain Charlotta, at your service!
Hm... I hope I'm wrong, and everything's dandy.
There's no time to waste. People are counting on us!
There's no better feeling than helping people with my fists!
Well, we goin' goblin hunting or what?
I smell burning wood on the breeze... We must make haste.

This goddess of alchemy and ten-star cutie will solve all
your problems!
Hmph. Onward.

When you're ready, let's go search for more of those
stragglers!
I'm worried about those poor people. Let's hurry!
Just a moment!

This here's hallowed ground. A special aura keeps the monsters at
bay.

If you need to rest, find this crystal. You can even stock up on
supplies and fix up your weapons.
We're counting on you!
Eeeek!
Uh-oh! Look!
Don't get cold feet now! We need to help, stat!
Hellooo? We need to move! Those people are in trouble!
H-help! Please...
Well... lookie here.
We're feastin' today!

Dirty goblins! Step away from the islanders, or you'll be
sorry!

How dare they prey on the unfortunate. Lyria, stay close to
me.
Buncha no good, lawless punks.
I've never met a goblin that's survived my magic!
Aw, cut the crap. Time to take out the trash.
You know, I think some corporal punishment is in order.
These hoodlums need to be taught a serious lesson.
Secure the islanders!
I've got it covered!
Your cruelty won't go unpunished.
I will put an end to this in one fell swoop. Come.
Defeating a horde of monsters is child's play!
Bad behavior has nasty consequences, y'know.
One cut, one kill.
Gahahaha! Cheeky little brats for me to punch!
Time to bash some skulls!
I'll handle them.
A quick game of whack-a-goblin couldn't hurt.
Enough is enough.

What's the matter? If you don't fight, these people are done
for!
Come in, come in. This is Rolan. Can anyone hear me?

Whoa! The homemade thingamabob actually works! We read
you loud and clear.
It sounds a bit noisy on your end.
Yeah! We're busy rescuing islanders from slash-happy goblins.
Wait, what! Are the people okay?

They've taken a number of hostages, but it won't stay that
way for long!
Please do everything you can to free them!
That's the spirit! Give 'em heck!
Gyahaha. Tasty prey here!
Reinforcements! Keep your heads on a swivel!
Hey! Where're you goin'? You can't abandon these people!
There. That's the last of them.
Now to set the captured people free!
Let's hurry and free those prisoners!
I really think we should help the islanders!
Oh no, pal. We can't leave until those islanders here are safe!
Oh no, pal. We can't leave until those islanders here are safe!
Everyone! Get on board!
We've been... saved?
Io, take care of their injuries!
I'm on it!
Thank you...
I'm just glad everyone's safe and sound.

What would we have done without your crew? Skyfarers are
somethin' else!

Thank you so much, everyone! But more settlements could
be under attack!
Better keep going! We gotta check on those people!
Are the erratic winds causing the goblins to act violently?

That's a big problem if true. Goblins don't usually go berserk
like average monsters.
This is Rolan. I see more captives up ahead!
Understood. Pick up the pace, everyone!
Something tells me these aren't normal goblins.

Maybe that's how they are in Zega, or it's the wind's fault.
Either way, watch out.

Wonder why the gobbers're going after settlements... They
usually steer way clear of towns.

With more people fleeing the area, they could see this as
their big chance to expand.

Doesn't this island remind you Port Breeze, back when we
met Rackam?
Oh yeah. That's when he convinced us to be an official crew!

I bet he was dying to join you guys. Where else would he find
cooler crewmates?
How would you know? You joined after me!
That's all for this area. Let's hurry to the next place!

I think we've swept this place good. Why don't we keep
going?
Let's head to that place Fix It Dude was talking about.

If I were captured, I'd totally want someone to come rescue
me. Hint, hint.
Whoa! Now that's what I call a view!

Weird, isn't it, how being up high gives you the urge to look
down?
It's scary looking down, but I can't help myself!
Hehe! Kablamo! That was a wicked sick shot!
Aww... Missed...
They have the high ground!
Thought they'd get the slip on us, did they?
Oh no... The bridges are in pieces...

We'll have to get our feet wet. Mind where you step,
everyone!
I'm moving as fast as I can! Keep those goblins occupied!
We will, Rolan. You just focus on flying.
Yes, but...
Never mind. You're right. I'll put my trust in you skyfarers.
There's more gobbos here! Take 'em out!
Hold up! Job's not done till the islanders are safe.
Oh, great. They know how to shoot bows.
They'll need time to reload. That's when we charge.
We've made a decent dent in their numbers. Keep at it.
We've cleared the area. It should be safe to free the captives.
Hey! You can't just wander off with lives on the line!
Come on, those poor people are waiting for us.
Thank goodness everyone's okay. Quickly! Get on board!
Don't worry, you're in good hands now.
Phew... Thanks...
I was so scared...
You did a great job holding out.
What a show! I'm so pumped up right now!
Uh... Maybe I healed him a little too much...
You did it! You saved everyone! Thank you!
Oh no! The windmills have come under attack!
Got it! Next destination is the windmill!
Oh no! The community by the waterfront is under attack!
Roger that! Next up is the waterfront!
It's just up ahead! Don't let the islanders down!
This way, right? Come on, you guys!

Remember, keep your eyes peeled for a windmill. That's our
stop.
Hey, pal, more prisoners are near the windmill. Don't forget.
Waterfront's waiting! Better get a move on!

Better get to the waterfront so's we can lend a claw! Now,
on the double!
All those burning houses... Those poor people.

Hurry, Io. We can't save their homes, but we can still save
their lives.
On it!

Damn bastards ruined the beautiful countryside. It's a cryin'
shame...
Yep. So let's do what we can to get things back to normal.
We have to get to the islanders.
I know how you feel, but don't stray too far, okay?
Okay... Just promise me you'll be careful too.

Man, doesn't matter which skydom we're in, we always end
up working, don't we?
C'mon, this is normal for us. Is it buggin' ya?
Not at all. I wake up every day ready for a new adventure.
None of us could ever ignore a cry for help!
Especially if a primal beast is behind the ruckus.
Right. That's also on our to-do list.
Timber wolves!
They've even learned how to tame wolves.
Gah! Can't get a bead on 'em!
I'll be there soon! Please hold out as best as you can!
Roger, dodger! We'll lock it down!
Looks like the goblins have hostages! We're on it!
Good find! Please, do your best to defend them!
Even burned that big windmill... How awful...

Calm down and observe its movements. It must have a
weakness.

Oh great, looks like some of them can use magic too. Don't
get sloppy now!
Hey, come back! We're not done saving the island yet!
Can you save any side trips for later? The islanders need us!
Can you save any side trips for later? The islanders need us!
Hell yes! Send those puppies scampering!
This goblin looks tough. Please be careful.
Tough, eh? I guess he works out in his spare time.
So who's got the bigger guns? Them or you?
Huh? Well, check this out. I mean it's me, right?
Watch out. This isn't your average goblin.
One more group accounted for!
Nice! Give 'em back that sweet, sweet freedom!
Whatever you're trying to pull, bud, islanders come first!
Those bonds look really painful. Let's undo them right away!
You're safe now. Hurry to the ship!
Thank goodness!
Don't give up, okay?
I'm... alive?
You're going to be fine.
Can ya walk, miss?
Thank you, thank you, thank you!
Those poor folk are safe thanks to you! Great job, everyone!
Hehe, all in a day's work!
Now, we should return to our search—
Huh? What the...

Heavens help us... There are others who haven't made it out
yet!
Oh no! This is awful!
You have to rescue them! I'll lead the way!
Got it! Full speed ahead, everybody!
I pray we're not too late!

Those poor souls are being attacked by goblins! Please get
to them as quickly as you can!

The villagers can't hold out on their own! We're their only
hope!
Right!
Will the islanders be okay?
They'll be better than okay once we bust in like heroes.
I think I sense a primal nearby!
Hold on to that thought! Freeing the prisoners comes first!
That's right!
We made it, Rolan! About to start fumigating the place.
Thanks, buddy! That puts my mind at ease!
Buddy? Seriously? I'm at least five years older than you.
You wouldn't believe how old I am.
Which would make you... how old?
My lips are sealed.

Push comes to shove, laugh in the face of danger, and show
your skyfaring spirit.
We're almost there! Push through!
Gah! Another heavyweight!
What, are these chuckleheads brothers or something?
Heh, they should've sent more than a trio!
Hold it! We can't just abandon these islanders!

What's the big idea? It's not like you to turn tail and run,
!
One down, two to go! Hold nothing back!
Only one left! You got this!
Yeah! And don't ever come back!
Phew... Really had our work cut out for us, huh?
I just hope the islanders are safe and sound.
Let's talk to the islanders and make sure they're okay.
Hey... Why don't we speak with the people we just saved?
Just who are you guys?
We're traveling skyfarers, and we're here to rescue you.
Chin up, everyone! Everything's going to be all right!
Wait... Was that Rolan?
Guess we really are saved.
Let's quickly get you aboard Rolan's ship—
No, wait! Listen to me!
We fled from the goblin fortress that lies deep in the nearby ruins.

But our friends are still in there, and they can't make it out on their
own...
What's the call, ?
Let's get those people out of there.
Hang on. We've still got loose ends here.
Let's get those people out of there.
Let's get those people out of there.
Hehe, I knew you'd say that, !
Come in, Fix It Dude!
Rolan here. What can Rolan do for you?

We're gonna break some people outta some goblin fortress, so
take care of things here!

Got it! I know this isn't what you signed up for, but... Just be careful
in there!
Will do! Who's ready to do this?
Hang on. We've still got loose ends here.
Hang on. We've still got loose ends here.

People are dependin' on us. Whatever you gotta do first, make it
quick.

Y'all think this is the goblin fort we're lookin' for? Gives me
the willies...
Be on guard.
Doesn't look very friendly...
Oh! We meet again.
Can I offer you a nice knickknack in these trying times?
It's eerily quiet...
Stop it!
That sounded like a kid.
Hurry!
Is this like... a coliseum?

You heard that screaming, right? It's gotta be more
islanders!

This place is crawling with goblins, but it doesn't seem like
they wanna scuffle.
No! Run! Get out while you still can!
That doesn't sound good!

That's one big, honkin' shield! Maybe it's best to hit it from
the back!

Quite the menacing shield. Let's work together to attack
from behind.

Something tells me this ain't gonna be a cakewalk! Avoid
head-on attacks, folks!
Is that a shield or a wall! That's gotta be cheating!

A shield like that, direct attacks won't do squat. If only we
could break it...

Well, someone's well-equipped. Crush the brute, and its
friends will surely cower.

It attacks friend and foe alike... This is no ordinary bad
guy—don't get careless!

A frontal attack will be ineffective... I'll create a diversion! On
me, everyone!

Hoo-buddy, that's one tough-lookin' shield. But I bet I'm
even tougher!

It seems we've found their ringleader. Good—allow me to
dethrone him!
A shield wielded improperly is mere decoration.

Quite the heavily armed goblin! But I shall take down this
goliath!

A battle of strength versus skill? Don't mind if I do,
hyuk-hyuk!
I'll make quick work of it!

Such armor will only bind you! A true giant tempers his
body, not his equipment!

This the head honcho? Sweet. Was looking for a new
punching bag!
That's an impressive shield... But it won't save you now.
Finally, an interesting opponent.
Cagliostro's gonna school you!
I will destroy you, shield and all.
This is Rolan! What's your status?
We're going toe to toe with this huuuge goblin jerk!
Roger that! I'm on my way; hold out until I arrive!

Damn, that was a good hit. It means business with that
shield.

That gobber charges like a wild boar, but I reckon we can
outmaneuver it!
The bigger they are, the harder they fall!
Where'd all the small fry come from?
You're wearing him down!
Keep slashing! The lug's on its last legs!
Here they come again! Watch your back!
Spread out and keep your distance!
Looks like it's losing steam... We should strike now.
Look! The shield is really battered now!
Hang on—do you think we can break it?
Heck yeah! We broke its shield!
Uh-oh, that means it's faster now! Watch out, guys!
Boo-yah! No grumpy gobbo's gonna one-up us!
Yeah, that's right! Run away with your tail between your legs!
Lyria, did you notice the wind throughout the battle?
Yes, I'm sure of it.
It has to be Tempeal's primal beast.
Bingo. Guess this is where the real battle starts.

Hello? Is everyone all right? What happened to the hostages in the
fortress?
Everyone's fine. They just need to rest.
Stay still!
Ow, ow...
We're alive...
Yeah...
What a relief. I can't thank you all enough.

So... What do you guys say to meetin' the blowhard stirrin' up this
storm?
Wait, what are you talking about, Rackam?

Told ya before we left Folca, remember? A problem with a primal is
our problem too.

I don't know about this... Maybe it's best to leave well enough
alone?
But if we don't calm down the primal beast...
The situation on the island is only going to get worse.
I hear what you're saying, but—
Trust us.
Trust us.
Think of the islanders' safety.
Trust us.
Trust us.

All right, I understand. I'm sure veteran skyfarers know what
they're doing.

All right, I understand. I'm sure veteran skyfarers know what
they're doing.
Think of the islanders' safety.
Think of the islanders' safety.
's right. These winds spell trouble for the entire archipelago.

You oughta fly the islanders back to Folca before it gets out of
hand.
Okay. Fair point.
I'll trust your judgment and get these poor souls to safety.

But if it gets risky, there's no shame in retreat. I still owe you a
reward.
You don't have to tell us twice! Thanks for the concern!
Sit tight. The least I can do is drop you off a little closer.
Heh... Reminds you of our showdown with Tiamat, doesn't it?
I was wondering why this felt so familiar.
Good luck and stay safe!
Man, those people we saved were so grateful.
Our job isn't over yet! Those winds are still a big problem!
You're not wrong!
Looks like a mining setup. Neat!
The winds have picked up.
Rather foreboding, isn't it? ...Let's hurry.

I think we're getting closer to the primal. Keep an eye out,
okay?
Whoa, this place gets way bigger on the inside.
Whoa... Look everyone!
Some sort of... Altar?
That's a primal beast!

One wrong move, and that could be us... Then we can forget
about ever making it home.
Furycane?
Huh?
That's its name. Just for a second, I could hear its whispers...
And it sounded so upset... It needs our help!
Our help with what, I wonder?

I suppose there's only one way to find out. Let's get closer,
so Lyria can attempt to soothe it.
I'll do my best!
It's getting more violent. We need to act quickly!

We need to stop the primal's rampage before it gets any
worse!
Look out!
Waaah! Holy...

We're not jumping across that gap. Let's find a safer way to
cross.
Let's keep our fingers crossed there's another way around.
Hey, you guys! Think we could go this way?
Why don't you try activating this thing?
Let's get a move on!
Ugh, more goons! Just our luck!

Do you think these goblins are running away from the primal
beast?
Sure seems that way.

But if we leave 'em be, they'll just try to ransack the town
again.
That should be the last of 'em.
Again with the goblins?!
There! Now it's a straight shot to the altar!
Come on! Let's not waste anymore time.
Poor thing... We have to help it.
Uh, think I'm having déjà vu, but there's another lever here!
Activate this sucker, and let's get a move on!
Hurry! The altar should be down this path!
It's the home stretch! Go, go, go!
Pick up the pace, people! But don't get blown away!
Oh crud! Watch out!
This thing's not gonna hold up much longer!
You've gotta be kidding!
Jump for it!
Wait, what! This is insane!
Look out!
We can take refuge in the back cave!
Now it's below us!
We're almost there!
Phew... Too many close calls lately...
Lyria, are you hurt?
No... I think.

Altar's above us, huh? Hope we've all got our hiking boots
on!

The altar was somewhere above here, I think. Is there a way
up?

Today's been one hell of a welcome to the skydom. Could we
have one normal day?

I mean, we are skyfarers. Kinda comes with the territory,
don't it?

Sure, but I don't know how many more death-defying 
escapades my heart can take.
The people of Tempeal must have been mining here...

I imagine so... Thanks to the primal, it looks like they've got
no shortage of resources.
Primals are amazing...
Haven't we been through enough of this already!

Looks like the only way left is up! Either we move it or lose
it, folks!
Poor thing... Stuck in a ceaseless rampage...
It's suffering a great deal.
We better move faster! It's too dangerous here!
The heck are you doin'! Move it!
Argh! Do these mangy things never learn or what?
What's become of them? Are they deranged?
I don't know, but they're tryin' to take us down with 'em.
Move! Don't let it catch you!
There's the exit! We're home free!
Man, I feel like my wings're gonna fall off...

What lies ahead may become unpredictable. Are you
prepared?

What lies ahead may become unpredictable. Are you
prepared?
C'mon. We've got this!
The wind's so strong...
Must be close to the eye of the storm. Be ready for a fight.
Yeah... C'mon, this ain't our first rodeo with a primal!

We'll just have to hold him off until Lyria can talk some sense
into it! Stay on your toes!

Taking control of a primal is no simple task. Could the
empire's dark essence have made it to this skydom? And
who brought it?

It's either you or us that's goin' down today—And, spoiler
alert, it ain't gonna be us!

We know you're suffering. Give us some time, and we'll
make you right as rain!

Forced to destroy the island you built. Can't say it gets more
pitiful 'n that.
You're going to be okay now. We're going to help you.

I can hear your crying, your lamenting. Don't worry. I'll free
you.

A dual-wielding primal beast. Let's see if my twin blades
match up to yours!
It must really hurt, huh? Well, feel free to vent at me!

You are bound by chains of agony. Allow the Lord of Flames
to liberate you!
I shall end this, I swear upon my sword.

To think such a huge primal could be controlled. This will
take all of my might!
Hm. Someone pulling yer strings? Maybe I can cut you loose!

Your delirious soul is but a nightmare. I shall cut the roots of
evil that bind it!

My fists are wailing! They quiver, ready to accept your
anguish!

Who says wild horses can't be tamed? Let's wrangle it,
Arvess!
It's my job to hunt primals like you. Sorry, nothing personal.

This bag of hot air isn't the problem. We can't let it bog us
down!
I'll settle this.
I don't think Furycane can hear me...

Is something blocking our connection? This is just like what
happened with Bahamut!

Well, we've dealt with rampaging primals before. We'll just
have to do it again!

Right. We'll chip away at its defenses until Lyria is able to
absorb its power!
Y-yeah...
Oh, Furycane... We're going to save you.
What a beast...
There is something... different about this primal.
Really? What's so special about it?
I can't say anything for certain. Furycane... What are you?

Phew all these rough winds... Kinda reminds you of Tiamat,
doesn't it?

Tiamat's anger was always motherly somehow... But
Furycane's gales seem to shriek with hate.
Please stop this! Furycane!
Best back off and watch its behavior for now!
Its magic's weaker... Lay it on, guys!
That's what I'm talking about! Send this windbag packing!
It stopped moving. Now's our chance!
It stopped moving again! Get 'em!
Its armor... It regenerated!
Still got a lotta fight left in ya, eh, bud?
Armor's up again! Back to square one!
Did it just summon a tornado?!
Careful, everyone! Don't get sucked in!
Here comes the whirlwind! Run for it!
Don't look now, but we've got a full-on double tornado!
Ngh, we'll never hit it at this rate!
It turned into a big wind bullet... How do you stop that?
I... I think I can help!
Ward of light... come forth!
Over here! Quickly!
You better stay in the bubble!
All right! Ready for some payback?
Thank you, Lyria. You were superb.
Hehe...
One more time... Haaah!
Furycane... I'm so sorry!
It worked!
Nice, it's wide open!
I'll protect everyone!
Yeah, sock it to 'em!
You're askin' for trouble if ya don't get inside Lyria's barrier!
Sorry! I'll try to time the next one better!
Thy name is... Bahamut!
You listened! Thank goodness!
Heh! Nice, Lyria! Glad he's fightin' on our side this time.
Focus! Furycane's power is starting to swell!
Hold up, did the demon pony just transform!?

It is a primal beast, after all. Were you expecting something
different?

You can tell primal beasts were weapons created by Astrals.
Their powers are capable of untold destruction.
But after the War they abandoned us here in the Sky Realm.

Some took to the land; some were deified. Still others found
a home alongside skydwellers and helped advance great
civilizations.

Like Furycane, the primal of vitality. It blessed Tempeal with
its power.

How callous it is to twist this creative soul into an
instrument of destruction.
Payback's on its way!

Darn right! Just don't get sloppy, 'cause this thing means
business!
Furycane... I promise we'll save you!

Its magic reserves are crazy! It keeps flinging attack after
attack at us!
Something about Furycane's power feels unnatural...
Huh? What do you mean?
I'm not sure, but something isn't right.
Those swirly balls look like bad news! Avoid 'em if you can!
Globes of doom incoming! Stay on your toes!
Boltnado's coming to fry our tails! Run!
Oh no! It's going to charge!
Heads up! Don't get caught flat-footed!
Um, this looks bad...
Oh no... Furycane, please don't!
The tornado's growing!
If we can just get past those winds somehow...
Wait for a gap to appear! That's our way in!
It's gathering power in its sword!
That's never a good thing! How do we get it to quit?
Furycane, no! You have to stop!

We're gonna get blown away at this rate! Head to the center
of the whirlwind!
It's charging its sword again! Be careful!
Everybody, scram!
Oh crud! Don't get diced!
Now we're getting somewhere!

Yeah. Furycane's weakened, and we're still breathing. That's
two wins.
